<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: cataphract armor -->
  <CataphractArmor.label>カタフラクトアーマー</CataphractArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Craft cataphract armor, heavy powered armor that slows the user but which can absorb extreme punishment. Note that these also require advanced components. -->
  <CataphractArmor.description>カタフラクトアーマーが製作可能になります.装着者を鈍重にしますが,極度の攻撃すら受け止める強力な装甲のヘビーパワーアーマーです.先進コンポーネントが必要になります.</CataphractArmor.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->cataphract armor</li>
    <li>subject_story->first developed [ANYPAWN_possessive] cataphract-equivalent armor as a method of exploring active volcanoes</li>
    <li>subject_story->was commissioned to produce custom sets of cataphract armor for Imperial boarding parties</li>
    <li>subject_story->fought with the rebels and studied the armor of a captured cataphract</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting cataphract armor</li>
  -->
  <CataphractArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->カタフラクトアーマー</li>
    <li>subject_story->活火山を探索する手段として,カタフラクトに相当するアーマーを最初に開発した</li>
    <li>subject_story->帝国軍の依頼を受けて,搭乗部隊用のカタフラクトアーマーのカスタムセットを作成した</li>
    <li>subject_story->反乱軍と共に戦い,捕らえたカタフラクトの着ている鎧を研究した</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->カタフラクトアーマーの作成</li>
  </CataphractArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: gunlink -->
  <Gunlink.label>ガンリンク</Gunlink.label>
  <!-- EN: Build wearable gunlinks to enhance your soldiers' shooting accuracy. -->
  <Gunlink.description>兵士の射撃精度を高める,着用できるガンリンクが作成可能になります.</Gunlink.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->accuracy enhancement</li>
    <li>subject_story->converted a glitterworld ocular implant into a more generic targeting computer</li>
    <li>subject_story->was happy at the performance of the factory's gunlinks, though the increased death rate due to helmet loss was troubling</li>
    <li>subject_story->bulk-purchased gunlinks for the snipers in the army, forbidding them to front-line soldiers</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->enhancing accuracy with gunlinks</li>
  -->
  <Gunlink.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->射撃精度向上</li>
    <li>subject_story->Glitterworldの視覚インプラントを,より汎用的のある照準コンピューターに改造した</li>
    <li>subject_story->工場生産したガンリンクの品質に満足した.しかし,ヘルメットを着用できないことによる死亡率の増加には常に悩まされていた</li>
    <li>subject_story->軍の狙撃兵のためにガンリンクを大量購入し,前線の兵士にはガンリンクの使用を禁止した</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->ガンリンクと射撃精度</li>
  </Gunlink.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: jump packs -->
  <JumpPack.label>ジャンプパック</JumpPack.label>
  <!-- EN: Build jump packs to perform aerial assaults during combat. -->
  <JumpPack.description>戦闘中に空中攻撃を行うジャンプパックが作成可能になります.</JumpPack.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->jump packs</li>
    <li>subject->short-distance flight</li>
    <li>subject_story->operated an entertainment park focused on extreme experiences, including boomrat petting and jump pack courses</li>
    <li>subject_story->ran mountaineering tours on low-grav planets, where jump packs and oxygen masks were mandatory</li>
    <li>subject_story->bypassed the turret defenses of officer training with a jump pack assault</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->performing aerial assaults</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting jump packs</li>
